HEADWORD: Numskull
<hw>Num"skull`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Numb</ets> +
<ets>skull</ets>.]</ety> <def>A dunce; a dolt; a stupid fellow.</def>
<altsp>[Also spelled <asp>numbskull</asp>.]</altsp>
<mark>[Colloq.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>They have talked like <qex>numskulls</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Arbuthnot.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Numskulled</ent>⟦br⟧
